{"tid":2361171,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[21年3月]AirPods Pro 2、iPhone SE(3代)、iPad mini(6代)、新iPad Pro","createTime":"2021-01-10T11:57:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T08:54:17.000Z","uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"978ec54464240b9859bf3da7de0da95d35f0559c","tid":2361171,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T11:57:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">AirPods Pro 2代藍牙耳機：充電盒與外觀重新設計</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n根據 Mac Otakara 引用中國供應鏈商消息，新款 AirPods Pro （第二代）充電盒將會重新設計，厚度保持 21 毫米，高度與寬度分別改為 46毫米和54毫米，與當前 AirPods Pro 充電和高度 45.2 毫米和寬度 60.6 毫米明顯有差異，這表明 AirPods Pro 2 代充電盒會因為耳機造型不同有所調整。<br />\n<br />\n近幾個月前有多方爆料消息全指出蘋果會在 2021 年推出 AirPods Pro 2代，像是彭博社 Mark Gurman 據知情人士得知，蘋果正研發 AirPods Pro 2代內部測試機已經取消機柄設計，具有更圓潤外觀，能夠讓耳塞成為一體式造型，機身遮住耳朵面積更大，類似三星、亞馬遜 Amazon Echo 和 Google 最新耳機外型，同時也保留備更換耳塞功能。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QOFjtrD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQOFjtrD.jpg&h=944204a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">iPhone SE 3 是延後推出 iPhone SE Plus</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n另外 Mac Otakara 也透露在 AirPods Pro 推出後，蘋果也會發表第三代 iPhone SE ，推出的時間剛好是在 2020年 4.7吋 iPhone SE 2代推出一年後，但是爆料並沒有談到設備細節。<br />\n<br />\n從過去消息來看，這款 iPhone SE 3 就是造成蘋果延後推出 5.5吋 iPhone SE Plus 設備，設計與 iPhone 8 Plus 類似。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><br />\n新款 iPad mini （第6代）類似 iPad Air 3 代設計</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n據 Mac Otakara 從中國供應鏈取得最新消息，新款 iPad mini （第6代）螢幕會採用8.4吋，取代舊款 iPad mini 5 的7.9 吋機種，同時外觀也會類似 iPad Air 3 代設計，採用全螢幕窄邊框設計，頂部電源鍵會結合 Touch ID 指紋辨識，以及沿用 Lightning 接孔設計。<br />\n<br />\niPad mini 從 2019 年推出後，歷經三年都沒有更新，且 iPad mini 外觀設計一用就是 7 年，這幾年大多都只是提升性能和部份規格，近年蘋果也開始替多款產品改用全螢幕設計，預計會在 2021 年 3 月春季發表會上推出新款 iPad mini 6 代。<br />\n<strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><br />\niPad Pro 2021</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/jon_prosser/status/1346616132262883331?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjon_prosser%2Fstatus%2F1346616132262883331%3Fs%3D21&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7R6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=b954a11b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjon_prosser%2Fstatus%2F1346616132262883331%3Fs%3D21&h=bd40d202\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/jon_prosser/status/1346616132262883331?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"628edf6e3c3bfed734cda1ad3a511bb9c07bcbf3","tid":2361171,"uid":109923,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T12:01:10.000Z","msg":"全部都好期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最佳孝機 - 平+大mon+易用嘅iOS：iPhone SE(第3代)<br />\n最強平板：A14x - iPad Pro 2021<br />\n最強扮工神器 - 細size平板：iPad mini(第6代)<br />\n技術終於成熟嘅ANC：AirPods Pro 2"},{"pid":"74b5094aa3e25e03539131a1aae7277b8d7898ec","tid":2361171,"uid":128600,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T12:18:05.000Z","msg":"等iphone se plus"},{"pid":"fc9d6d004eeaae5aa3f948f279e5ef29be0ae26b","tid":2361171,"uid":109923,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"74b5094aa3e25e03539131a1aae7277b8d7898ec","tid":2361171,"uid":128600,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T12:18:05.000Z","msg":"等iphone se plus"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T12:19:03.000Z","msg":"touch id<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70293e1b422a1e2fabf3ae879ccd3cdf149255eb","tid":2361171,"uid":25612,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T12:50:47.000Z","msg":"AirPods Pro 2 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11fe467267455bb1c5c6bb7f85e3df4db4f690fc","tid":2361171,"uid":2890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T02:43:13.000Z","msg":"ipad mini 呢個假希望仲要幾多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d44dc1cbf2d6f88611533d259686c09adf13e0c","tid":2361171,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score